      value: |
        For help with simple questions, visit the [Discord server](https://discord.gg/ZYrCacRuez) before opening an issue.

        Before opening an issue, please read this whole form and ensure you:
        * Have updated to the latest version
        * Read the [FAQ](https://github.com/TakosThings/Fluent-Discord/wiki/FAQ) and other help articles on the [Wiki](https://github.com/TakosThings/Fluent-Discord/wiki)
        * Disable all plugins. Open a [Plugin Compatibility Request](https://github.com/TakosThings/Fluent-Discord/issues/new?assignees=&labels=better+discord%2Cplugin+compatibility&template=plugin_compat.yml&title=Plugin+name+here) instead if the plugin is not already on the [compatible list](https://github.com/TakosThings/Fluent-Discord/wiki/Plugin-Compatibility).
        * Have searched and made sure your issue hasn't been reported before

        * Make sure to give your bug a descriptive title
  - type: textarea
    arrtibutes:
      label: Description
      description: What is wrong, and why is it incorrect?
